title: Zeit Z. Eisenhower 10/6: Trump Latest, Eddie Van Halen, Big Mike, Section 230, Pentagon Quarantine
itunes:title: Zeit Z. Eisenhower 10/6: Trump Latest, Eddie Van Halen, Big Mike, Section 230, Pentagon Quarantine
description:
On this edition of Zeit Z. Eisenhower Jack and Miles discuss the latest with Trump and his response to COVID-19, Eddie Van Halen has passed away, Trump supporters are trolling Michelle Obama, Trump is calling to "REPEAL SECTION 230" of the Communications Decency Act, and the Pentagon has gone into quarantine.
